Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:31.82,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Girls' Last Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Iiit's soooo daaaark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, can I turn on the lantern?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know where we'll find\Nthe next refueling station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've been in the dark for a while,\Nso my eyes might've gotten used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen the light of day in a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even know how many days it's been.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But seriously, where are we right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd we get into this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Yuu, who do you think it was\Nwho said they wanted to go into the hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was you, Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, that's an old saying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it go, "I wish I could just climb into a hole"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean it that literally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In either case, we've gotta find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have that much food left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even if we get outta here,\Nwe don't know if we'll find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When will we get to the top of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll sleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the soup like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so smooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's so thick...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we go the way the wind's blowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll find a way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bright, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nighttime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, since we finally made it outside,\Nlet's have some soup, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, just to celebrate getting out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be good now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our last can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew nighttime was this bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we were in that\Ndark cavern that whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It made us sensitive to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's gonna happen to us when the sun rises?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll burn to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Starry Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:10.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,War
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can keep on going if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna shoot, Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a terrible shot, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't carry a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them are just junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I could go look for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be a weapon.\NWe might find something we could use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if we're looking for food here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll either find something like rations, or find...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you think a tank tastes good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a big weapon graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,People long ago didn't have enough food, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So why'd they build all these weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they'd preserved food instead of making weapons,\Nour lives would be so much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they had their own problems, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it really fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fly too, right, Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a weapon, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was probably a bomber or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,War means killing one another, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno. Their interests probably didn't\Ncoincide with... the other side's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So like, if there are three people,\Nbut only enough food for two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that's when you've gotta\Nget your weapon and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Same now, same then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lotta different kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Chi, this looks real powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something else we could use\Nway more than that... there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. We can use them to move stuff\Nin our way or break down walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take as much as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chi, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's grab them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's not gonna fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to fly, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it can totally fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your half.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Says it's chocolate flavored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea what chocolate is, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A pack of five? An odd number...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll split it in half and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I should've carried a weapon too, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You actually ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You little, you little!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,That actually hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You little, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,J-just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved around too much and now I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The snow's yummy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to eat snow of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,War really is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
